items.text: DOD assessing critical materials supply chain vulnerability - rare earth elements, semiconductors key focus. GAO report highlights national security risks in strategic resource procurement (GAO)
UK commits $681M additional defense package to UKRAINE - supports ongoing military operations against RUSSIA; brings total 2024 military aid to ~$1.5B (Anadolu Agency)
US PENTAGON preparing contingency plans for potential extended military engagement with IRAN - significant escalation signals high-risk regional conflict scenario (Reuters)
UK commits £400M to long-range weapons procurement, signals expanded EUROPEAN defense cooperation - strategic investment in military capabilities (UK MoD)
U.S. PENTAGON preparing multi-week military contingency operation targeting IRAN — potential escalation in regional tensions following recent proxy conflicts and maritime incidents (Jerusalem Post)
USS GERALD R. FORD carrier strike group deployed to CARIBBEAN waters - first such positioning in recent years, signals potential VENEZUELA/regional tensions (PBS)
U.S. NAVY deploys second aircraft carrier to PERSIAN GULF — signals heightened military readiness against IRAN tensions (Source: Google Middle East)
CUBA's MATANZAS oil refinery suffers major fire — significant damage to critical fuel infrastructure amid ongoing economic crisis; potential supply disruption imminent (Al Jazeera)
U.S. INDOPACOM signals strong support for PHILIPPINES amid CHINA maritime tensions at Second Thomas Shoal - reaffirms defense commitment in strategic South CHINA Sea region (PACOM)
IDF captures key HAMAS operative linked to deadly 2025 shooting attack in ISRAEL - suspect believed to be close associate of original gunman (Yahoo)
PERU Congress to initiate presidential removal proceedings against Jose Jeri - corruption allegations surface 4 months after taking office (Al Jazeera)
PENTAGON temporarily lists 5 CHINESE defense firms as military-linked entities, abruptly withdraws filing — potential diplomatic signaling ongoing (SCMP)

CHINA continues military preparations around TAIWAN - ISW reports sustained pressure campaign with increased naval and air force exercises near Taiwan Strait, signaling potential escalation of regional tensions (ISW)
RUSSIA: Former KALASHNIKOV CONCERN director KSENIA GRASHCHENKOVA detained on power abuse charges in MOSCOW — placed in pretrial custody (TASS)
U.S. SPACE FORCE to absorb ARMY and NAVY satellite communications (SATCOM) mission areas - significant military reorganization of space-based infrastructure (INDOPACOM)
ISRAEL not consulted on U.S. potential military action against HOUTHIS - simultaneous airstrikes hit SANAA, YEMEN as diplomatic tensions escalate in RED SEA region (Jerusalem Post)
U.S. MILITARY transfers 5,700 ISIS detainees from SYRIA to IRAQ — major counterterrorism logistics operation completed, reduces detention strain in northeast SYRIA (AP)
TRUMP calls for IRAN regime change in direct statement - suggests US policy shift toward more aggressive stance against ISLAMIC REPUBLIC (NYT)

US MILITARY conducts lethal strike on boat in CARIBBEAN - 3 killed, part of ongoing maritime interdiction operations targeting suspected smuggling routes. Total maritime casualties now exceed 130 since September (Al Jazeera)

SUDAN conflict enters critical phase: 80% population now requires humanitarian aid, UN warns of potential widespread famine - massive displacement, 9M+ people forced from homes since conflict began in APRIL 2023 (UN OCHA)
INDIA finalizes $40B arms procurement deal: 114 RAFALE fighter jets from FRANCE, largest single combat aircraft purchase in recent military procurement history (Defense Express)

FORTEM Technologies awarded multimillion-dollar contract to provide counter-drone security for 2026 FIFA WORLD CUP venues across UNITED STATES, MEXICO, CANADA — protecting stadiums from potential aerial threats (Santa Maria Times)
TRUMP administration considered advanced F-35 fighter jet sale to SAUDI ARABIA — potential regional balance of power shift raises ISRAEL security concerns (Jerusalem Post)
RUSSIA economy: Finance Minister RESHETNIKOV expects inflation to slow to near 4% target, current annual rate at 6.4% (TASS)
RUSSIA-UKRAINE TALKS: Senior diplomat RYABKOV says Abu Dhabi remains preferred venue for next peace negotiations, dates still under discussion (TASS)
RUSSIA's HIGH-PRECISION SYSTEMS displays weapons at SAUDI defense expo in RIYADH: Thousands view military tech at World Defense Show (TASS)
RUSSIA warns potential US military intervention in IRAN now "entirely possible" - Senior diplomat RYABKOV signals heightened regional tensions (TASS)
LOCKHEED MARTIN secures new defense contract with US PENTAGON - profit-sharing agreement boosts investor confidence in defense sector (Reuters)
BARBADOS: PM MIA MOTTLEY wins landslide election, BARBADOS LABOUR PARTY secures all 30 parliamentary seats in historic victory (Guardian)
HUNGARY warns EU sanctions against RUSSIA's ROSATOM could halt Paks nuclear plant expansion project - SZIJJARTO warns of potential energy disruption (TASS)
